CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

June 9, 2014

[Cite as 06/09/2014 Case Announcements #2, 2014-Ohio-2484.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2014-0197. Disciplinary Counsel v. Smith.

This cause is scheduled for oral argument on Tuesday, June 10, 2014. Upon consideration of respondent’s expedited motion for continuance of oral argument, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
